data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bath brick house is located in the country, offering an open floor plan and a beautiful kitchen. The home is well taken care of and the backyard provides plenty of room to enjoy the peace and quiet of the country. Whether you're looking for a place to call home or a place to escape, this house is sure to meet your needs. Less then 30 minutes from Panama City. This home is eligible for USDA 100% financing 0 money down!
